{"tid":667091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旅保索償投訴飆68% 收費最貴≠保障最大","createTime":"2018-05-16T12:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T14:40:18.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc55c736d8a8a4274b921f2ebd413e5455529ded","tid":667091,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180516/20392359?_ga=2.219115609.1590170431.1526094399-1494298709.1503827088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F20392359%3F_ga%3D2.219115609.1590170431.1526094399-1494298709.1503827088&d=qOvJIoHipGfKSpPHgSLS3ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=28dd8a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F20392359%3F_ga%3D2.219115609.1590170431.1526094399-1494298709.1503827088&h=ed1d8ddd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180516/20392359?_ga=2.219115609.1590170431.1526094399-1494298709.1503827088</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】A太太偕老公遠飛葡萄牙開心自駕遊，駛到景點就泊好車，放下貴重財物在車尾箱，便急不及待把臂漫步。夫婦暢遊半小時後回來取車，驚覺車尾箱被人爆開，發現財物不見了。二人買了旅遊保，又馬上報警，以為可以獲得賠償，怎料保險公司以他們把財物放在無人看管的車輛內，不屬保障範圍而拒賠。這是消委會接獲的真實個案，該會今年首四個月接獲24宗旅保投訴，涉及保費和索償爭拗、不滿拒絕賠償及賠償不足等，2017年投訴個案達96宗，較2016年的57宗上升68%。"},{"pid":"d47aa427d4908b0531bcf98c89b78da8daff666a","tid":667091,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"即係放係酒店保險箱被爆都唔會賠"},{"pid":"c00ac26720d2a617a4460d0c56eb2444795f5460","tid":667091,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"咩冇人看管係唔受架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cb5b61236655ee17c018b941726dac347bea66","tid":667091,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf165176e802d3ad1abf370017f88cf087e1a3e9","tid":667091,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"Claim旅遊保險真係要睇清楚條款先好填form<br />\n無人看管，個人疏忽都唔保，好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}